juicyExplainer.paragraph1: $JUICY is the revenue token that powers this app. When you pay into Juicy Vision, you receive $JUICY tokens proportional to your contribution.
juicyExplainer.paragraph2: As the balance grows, so does the value backing each token. You can cash out anytime for your share, or hold to support the community business.
juicyExplainer.paragraph3: We run extremely lean, but paying for LLM tokens is expensive for now. Revenue from the app mostly flows back to $JUICY holders, guaranteed. The more value created, the more everyone benefits. We're in this together.
juicyExplainer.poweredBy: Uses revnets, powered by Juicebox, secured by Ethereum, Optimism, Base, and Arbitrum.
